title: Fennel and Sultana Rye Bread
ingredients: ['2 (7g) sachets dried active baking yeast', '250ml lukewarm water', '1L warm water', '1 tablespoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground ginger', '2 tablespoons caster sugar', '8 tablespoons fennel seed', '5 tablespoons black treacle', '1 tablespoon melted butter', '200g rye flour', '250g sultanas', '1.2kg bread flour']
